comments: Nice study. Thank you and good luck!

I enjoyed taking the time to add my opinion on this study. I look forward to doing more in the future.

This was an interesting study to go through, and I enjoyed watching the videos to see the development of the group's shorthand as well as seeing who guessed (in)correctly.  Thank you for your time, and best wishes on your study!
